Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: City plaza is an 19-story, Class A office tower located in the heart of Orange County’s Central County submarket. Located at the interchange of the 5, 57 and 22 Freeway, City Plaza offers exceptional signage opportunities with more than 410,000 vehicles that pass by daily. The property’s central location provides unparalleled access to all points of Orange County, Los Angeles County and Riverside County and sits between John Wayne International Airport and Long Beach Airport providing flexibility for today’s corporate traveler. Step outside your front door and into the thriving fresh air retail center where employees can grab a bite to eat, run errands and live a truly centered and healthy work life balance. City Plaza, perfectly centered.
